      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/43028.Upamanyu_Chatterjee">About Upamanyu Chatterjee</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/43028.Upamanyu_Chatterjee"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1260529826p3/43028.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/43028.Upamanyu_Chatterjee">Upamanyu Chatterjee
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
163
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14349358628491005548">Upamanyu Chatterjee is an Indian author and administrator, noted for his works set in the Indian Administrative Service. He has been named Officier des Arts et des Lettres (Officer of the Order of Arts and Letters), by the French Government.</span>

</div>
</div>

